'''Amzaz amɣribi amuri''' nɣ '''Amussu amuri''' (s [[Tutlayt Taɛrabt|taɛrabt]]: التيار المغربي الموري) iga yan umussu adlsan [[Lmɣrib|amɣribi]] iswwrin g yigr n [[Tasertit|tsrtit]], amzaz ad ila kraḍ iwtta: 
*Tamɣrabit,
* Timmuzɣa,
*Lmɣrib ad izwarn iggra.
Inbdadn n umzaz amɣribi gan iɛrrimn imɣribin iwsin ssiɛr i [[Tamazirt|tmazirt]] d umzruy-ns zɣ uzmz n tgldit i [[Muriṭanya|Muritanya]] ar wassad.

==Asisn ==
#Amzaz amɣrabi amuri, iga yat tsntayt n tusna d umzruy t tmagit tamɣṛibit g iman n tɛurmiwin, tamazirt n Lmɣrib tga yat tmazirt ur igin zun d kullu timizar yaḍnin, g umzruy nns d yilsawn ass iggudin aya ad as ican yat taṭfi i tmazirt,
#Amzaz amɣṛabiy amuriy igat yan uskkin iswurin g tama n tɣrma n tmazirt n umaɣṛib, imk inna iswuri bac ad izddy ingr tɛurmiwin s umata, mcinnai nna ira sg iskkin n usnflul g tẓuṛi d tusna.
#Ad rarin taɣṭft rarin uddur i tmaggit tamɣrabyt tgt tmaziɣt lli igan askkin isarsn izuran nns g wakal n tmazirt ad. mcinnai nna nna ixs ad nisin inafuln tgga tɣṛma tamɣrabit tamuriyt g umzruy is tga asagm n usirw n tmaggit tamaziɣt tamɣrabit.
#Amzaz islkn f usnumml "amuriy iymɣrabiyn lli mi tzdy tɣrma ns ttin tgldit n muritanya d lmɣrib, ayad n tamunt yudjad ad tg tmazirt nɣ yat g tmizar dar illa umzruy igudin g uẓawan nɣd g uswingm ula ṛcm g lrni aqbur imcinna,  a imcinnana az ar ittinni tamazirt n lmɣrib is tga yat tmazirt dar illa wuddur sg tusna nɣd amzruy nst mi gan izuran nss sg tmazirta.
#Imcinna tga tzdayt illan ingr ass d tɣrma yaṭnin yat tzrayt iḥlan, ur djin illi lmɣrib ddaw awd yat tdlsa n awd yat tawwunkt
#Ayad ayd ira uwzaz amɣṛabiy g wulawn n imuriyn imɣrabiyn, ad ur akkan i awd yat tdlsa tabrraniyt adɣaṛ g tmazirt nssn.
#Awttaz n umzaz amɣrabiy amuriy f ibrdan n izrfan.

== Tannayt nnsn ==
#  Asnfl sg umzruy amɣṛibi inzɣan sg umzruy n tɣrmi sg uzmz n tyldit/tgldit tamuritaniyt ar assa,
#  Ad nsksiw tanga n umzruy is iga yat tsaɣult tawssant i imɣrabiyn s yat twuri izddign
#  Igm g tzrawin timassanin nskrisn kan twuri asd iruran uddur i tmaziɣt g lmaɣṛib.
#  Ad nrar uddur i tutlayt tamaziɣt is tga tutlayt tansliyt i imɣrabiyn nttat d izuṛan nss.
#  Arari f kul isnubcn ittugan f tmaziɣt.
#  Ur nttadja awd yan ad iswuri awal n tutlayt i twuri igan tins
#  Ixssa imɣrabiyn ad issin tamurkist na nnan ad idir ig ur cin uddur i tusna nssn
#  Ad ur ikjjm g tmukrisin igan tin usɣan nɣd tin usrtiy ، imkinna ur iri ad ittili g tmukrisin igan tin iqbiln lli ittawin s bttu ingr ifgan.
#  Ig nra ad nrar uddur i tmazirt at tili ingr tmizar yaṭnin ixssa ad nuɣul s amzruy nɣ
#  Tga tutlayt tamaziɣt g tmazirt asnks axatar xss at nḥṭu.
#  Tasrut n amurwakuc(lmɣrib) afad ad yar addud nns gr iydudn d tmura niḍn ntta d amzruy nns amqaran iqnn s tmagit tamɣlnt
#  Ad nrzu tizi d umyawaz zi ku yan dars amyawad d umswal ibbihi
#  Amzruy amuri illa d uday d aṛumiy d amimunslm ntta akk itaḍf s umzruy adɣrn
#  Tga tutlayt tamziɣt igr n tuɣnsa n tbridt tangamt amuri
#  Iga uḥṭṭu n tutlyt tmnḍt d yat n tbridt i tgumi n tutlyt tanawayt
#  Abrid n tnbaḍt mamk ma illa ur izmar ad iffɣ f tmggit tmaziɣt

== Tasgiwin n isntayn :==
#  Isntayn n tukdut d izrfan n ufgan askkin n umrara n wawal, ur illi udɣar iwnna iran ad ismzgal ingr ufggan.
#  Iwaliwn ixwan ur illi udɣaṛ nssn g umrara n wawal,
#  Asnufl n yili n wawal d tussna n tmaziɣt sg zik ula assad.
#  Ad ng awal nɣ d umrara n rray yat twuri ibnnun ittawin s dat.
#  Aṛzzum n tbadutin n umsawaṭ iswurin d willi iswurin g lham n tusna n tmaziɣt.
#  Awzaz ar iswuri ar ittaws willi iswurin g lham d iwaliwn lli f yuwi udris.

